  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0ddd \u0d9c\u0dd8\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae \u0d9c\u0dd1\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dca 113 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc5\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "113 per liter domestic gas down by Rs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Muditha Peiris, Chairman of Litro Gas Company, said this morning (5) that the price of a 12.5 kg cylinder of Litro domestic gas has been reduced by 113 rupees.",
        "With this price reduction, the price of a 5 kg cylinder has been reduced by 45 rupees, and the price of a 2.3 kg cylinder has been reduced by 21 rupees and the new price will be effective from midnight today (5), said Mr. Muditha Peres.",
        "With this new price revision, the price of a 12.5 kg cylinder which was Rs.4664 has come down to Rs.4551.",
        "The price of a 5 kg cylinder which was 1872 rupees has been reduced to 1827 rupees, and the price of a 2.3 kg cylinder has been reduced to 848 rupees which was 869 rupees."
      ],
